creator: Elisabeth Charlotte Pauline Guizot
description:
LibriVox recording of Moral Tales by Elisabeth Charlotte Pauline Guizot. (Translated by Mrs. L. Burke.)
Read in English by Cate Barratt
Short stories written by the first wife of French statesman Francois Guizot for young readers. - Summary by Cate Barratt
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
